<div class="media-wrapper"><img src="https://cdn.macstories.net/apple-wwdc25-design-awards-hero-1748970470640.jpg" alt=""><p class="image-caption"></p></div>
<p id="p2">As WWDC approaches,&nbsp;<a href="https://developer.apple.com/design/awards/" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apple has announced</a>&nbsp;the finalists for its annual Apple Design Awards, and in a departure from recent years, the winners too.</p>
<p id="p3">This year, there are six categories, and each category has a winning app and game, along with four finalists. Unlike last year, there is no Spatial Computing category this year. The 2025 ADA winners and finalists are:</p>
<h3 id="delight-and-fun">Delight and Fun</h3>
<p id="p4"><strong>Winners</strong>:</p>
<ul id="ul5"><li>App
<ul><li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/capwords-ai-snap-learn-langs/id6738896465" rel="noopener noreferrer">CapWords</a> by HappyPlan Tech</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Game
<ul><li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/balatro/id6502453075" rel="noopener noreferrer">Balatro</a> by LocalThunk</li>
</ul></li>
</ul><p id="p6"><strong>Finalists</strong>:</p>
<ul id="ul7"><li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/lumy/id908905093" rel="noopener noreferrer">Lumy</a>&nbsp;by Raja V</li>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/denim-playlist-cover-maker/id1532250420" rel="noopener noreferrer">Denim</a>&nbsp;by Feel Good Tech</li>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/thank-goodness-youre-here/id6504887308?mt=12" rel="noopener noreferrer">Thank Goodness You&rsquo;re Here!</a>&nbsp;by Panic</li>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/prince-of-persia-lost-crown/id6504011865" rel="noopener noreferrer">Prince of Persia: The Lost Crown</a>&nbsp;by Ubisoft Montpellier</li>
</ul><h3 id="innovation">Innovation</h3>
<p id="p8"><strong>Winners</strong>:</p>
<ul id="ul9"><li>App
<ul><li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/play-create-better-apps/id6669873480?l=en-US" rel="noopener noreferrer">Play</a>  by Rabbit 3 Times</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Game
<ul><li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pbj-the-musical/id6499055208" rel="noopener noreferrer">PBJ &mdash; The Musical</a> by  Philipp Stollenmayer</li>
</ul></li>
</ul><p id="p10"><strong>Finalists</strong>:</p>
<ul id="ul11"><li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/moises-the-musicians-app/id1515796612" rel="noopener noreferrer">Moises</a>&nbsp;by Music.AI</li>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/capybara-ai-meeting-translator/id6667094162" rel="noopener noreferrer">Capybara</a>&nbsp;by Digital Workroom Ltd</li>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pawz-meditate-together/id6593665132" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pawz</a>&nbsp;by Bootloader Studio Holdings Private Limited</li>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/gears-goo/id6471676214" rel="noopener noreferrer">Gears &amp; Goo</a>&nbsp;by Resolution Games AB</li>
</ul><h3 id="interaction">Interaction</h3>
<p id="p12"><strong>Winner</strong>:</p>
<ul id="ul13"><li>App
