<p id="p24"><strong>Winners</strong>:</p>
<ul id="ul25"><li>App
<ul><li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/feather-draw-in-3d/id6737254232" rel="noopener noreferrer">Feather: Draw in 3D</a> by Sketchsoft</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Game
<ul><li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/infinity-nikki/id6502622570" rel="noopener noreferrer">Infinity Nikki</a> by Infold Games </li>
</ul></li>
</ul><p id="p26">Finalists:</p>
<ul id="ul27"><li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/mn/app/vocabulary-learn-words-daily/id1084540807" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vocabulary</a>&nbsp;by Monkey Taps</li>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/cellwalk/id1627776848" rel="noopener noreferrer">CellWalk</a>&nbsp;by Timothy Davison</li>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/control-ultimate-edition/id6502953520?mt=12" rel="noopener noreferrer">Control Ultimate Edition</a>&nbsp;by Remedy Entertainment PLC</li>
<li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/neva/id6737359999?mt=12" rel="noopener noreferrer">Neva</a>&nbsp;by Developer Digital</li>
</ul><p id="p28">The winners and finalists include a broad range of games and apps, including some from smaller developers including <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/lumy/id908905093" rel="noopener noreferrer">Lumy</a>, <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/denim-playlist-cover-maker/id1532250420" rel="noopener noreferrer">Denim</a> <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/art-of-fauna-cozy-puzzles/id1630468596" rel="noopener noreferrer">Art of Fauna</a>, <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/skate-city-new-york/id6448986810" rel="noopener noreferrer">Skate City: New York</a>, as well as titles from bigger publishers.</p>
<p id="p29">I&rsquo;m glad that Apple has announced the finalists for the last few years. Winning an ADA is a big achievement for any developer, but it&rsquo;s also nice to know who the finalists are because it&rsquo;s quite an honor among the many apps that could have been chosen, too. Plus as a fan of apps, Apple&rsquo;s longer finalist list always reminds me of an app or two that I haven&rsquo;t tried yet. Congratulations to all of this year&rsquo;s Apple Design Award winners and finalists.</p>
